<br>
I'm not going to quit if a slow component goes in, or if they make the spell more resistable or whatever else is on Test.. if the problem is that all the enchanters are soloing though, just turn things back the way they were before, then they make charmed pets take half the experience when solo unless you personally do over half the damage.  Doing that would encourage grouping, where everyone then benefits from your powerful pet.<br>
