<br>
Finally, the no-haste nerf won't stop me from soloing. I will still charm in HoH, and I will still get good experience. Basically instead of being able to do 3 mobs with one hasted pet, I may be reduced to 2 mobs per un-hasted pet. We shall see.<br>
